sentences.en: Laboratory testing included sieve analyses and unconfined compressive strength testing.
sentences.cn: 实验室测试包括筛分析及无侧限抗压强度测试.

sentences.en: Linda's unconfined hair fell to her shoulders.
sentences.cn: 琳达那未束的头发,散落在她的肩膀上.

sentences.en: One of the two main types of aquifer is the unconfined aquifer.
sentences.cn: 非承压含水层是两种主要含水层之一.

sentences.en: The aquifer is unconfined locally and may be recharged.
sentences.cn: 含水层因为局部不承压而得到补给.

sentences.en: There are three types of aquifers: perched, unconfined, and confined.
sentences.cn: 含水层有三种形态, 分别是上层滞水 、 潜水和承压水.

sentences.en: Unconfined water is abundance but confined water is scarcity.
sentences.cn: 地下潜水较多而承压水少.
